Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:26152,27986}Brother… why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:47086,50952}I'm so jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:50952,54552}I'm so jealous…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:54552,59219}I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:69886,74052}Although connected to this world,\Nthey do not belong to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:74052,78386}Although connected to that world,\Nthey do not belong to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.38,0:01:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:78386,82919}Anger, revenge, malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:82919,88952}No matter what form evil takes,\Nthey shall get rid of it in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.95,0:01:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:88952,92786}The guardian deities of the modern world:\Nthe Pi-hyoro family!
