Comment: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:55.38,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:175386,175386}Main part
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:03:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176286,180386}Kyōta, your part time job\Nbrings us a lot of popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180386,184219}Today, at the funeral ceremony,\Nthe guests addressed me as "high priest".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184219,187386}Believe it or not, but back in the day\NI even deserved that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187386,190186}Aren't you forgetting\Nsomething, Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190186,192286}What are you reaching out\Nthat hand for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192286,193686}For my paycheck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193686,196986}Ah yes, it completely\Nslipped my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198486,201986}Guess what I got here!\NA love letter to my handsome grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204052,206852}Have you got no sense of humor, Kyōta?\NIt's the next order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206852,208019}Order?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208019,210719}Yes. An old friend\Nof mine spoke to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210719,217486}He said that it is something that\Nonly our Pi-hyoro family can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219552,223319}Over the past year, four double suicides\Nhave occurred on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223319,228319}According to the old man,\Nour client, Mr. Ikuhashi Genpei,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228319,233286}is so wealthy that the people\Nliterally worship him on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233286,237286}And it was him\Nwho invited us there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:04:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237286,240952}Kyōta, I feel we've stumbled on\Nsomething noteworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240952,242252}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242252,243619}So do we take this order?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243619,245586}Of course we take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245586,250552}That's great. The next destination of the\NPi-hyoro family is the Ruōgi Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:16.55,Default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:251086,256552}{\fad(500,0)}"Black Revenge"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262952,266019}So cool! Grandpa\Nhas a nose for customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266019,269919}Sea and mountains as far as\Nthe eye can see. Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269919,270919}Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272086,275186}– Let's take a look!\N– Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275186,277186}Gosh, these goofs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283819,288586}Strange… We were supposed to be picked up\Nby someone from the Ikuhashi estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288586,292786}The boat comes here only once a day,\Nso they couldn't mistake the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294086,296186}Excuse me, are you from\Nthe Hōnenji Temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296186,298119}Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298119,302086}You look amazingly young,\Nhigh priest Ryūnen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302086,303686}"High priest Ryūnen"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306119,309019}Are you suggesting\NI'm that stinking…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311952,314086}For the love of Buddha,\Nwhere are your manners?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314086,316752}I apologize for the behavior\Nof my younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316752,322186}We are here on behalf of the high priest\Nand we will carry out the exorcisms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322186,323586}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323586,325886}No, I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325886,330286}I am the personal doctor of\NMr. Ikuhashi Genpei. My name is Kariya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330286,332586}And you, their doctor,\Npick us up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332586,334886}Please follow me to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334886,336952}In fact, we're still waiting…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336952,339786}Kyōta, this car can fit\Nup to four people, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340486,341986}Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341986,344786}Ah, absolutely not.\NWe're getting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349019,350319}Ah, Kyōta-niichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350319,352519}Kibatta-neechan!\NWait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:06:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355486,360086}We are not to tell anyone\Nthat we are psychics? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360086,365986}In fact, Mr. Genpei and I are the only\Npeople who know about your visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365986,367686}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367686,371552}The grandson of the owner, Takahiko-kun,\Nhates any mentions of the supernatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371552,373086}I am very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373086,376086}That won't be a problem.\NWe don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376252,379652}I see that Mr. Ikuhashi trusts you,\Nhis doctor, in many matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379652,382786}Actually, I am half his advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382786,385052}By Buddha's loafers!\NWhat a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385052,387252}A magnificent residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387252,390652}Who would have thought that this island\Nwould hide such a beautiful mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390652,397219}I heard that the Ikuhashi family built\Ntheir fortune in the arms industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397219,398419}This way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398419,401552}The arms industry, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407219,409552}It won't be a simple job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414586,417186}{\i1}What was that nasty presence?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:07:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417186,421086}{\i1}Did it come from the garden?\NOr maybe from this property?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432986,435786}Thank you for coming\Nall the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435786,438086}I am Ikuhashi Genpei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438086,443152}I am Shinohara Ryōko, and this is\Nmy younger brother, Kyōta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443152,444386}Nice to meet you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444386,450719}I am pleased to meet the exorcists who\Nare recommended by Mr. Ryūnen himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450719,453219}Let us get to the point.\NPlease tell…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453219,454486}Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454486,456019}Takahiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456019,458552}I heard noise.\NWe have guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458552,462352}Ah, these are my friend's grandchildren\Nwho are visiting the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462352,464419}Meet my grandson, Takahiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464419,465852}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467052,472586}Takahiko, shouldn't you be\Nstudying with your teacher now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472586,475452}I fired him some time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475452,476819}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:08:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476819,480952}This guy claimed that our island\Nis in the clutches of evil spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480952,485652}He kept going on how these spirits\Nwere to be behind these recent suicides.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485652,489419}I won't let anyone who talks\Nsuch nonsense teach me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491952,497086}Anyway, I'm talking to our\Nguests now. Go to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497086,498552}Grandpa…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502086,505252}Kyōta, kids like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505252,508786}Eh, you always push\Neverything on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510386,514419}Takahiko-kun, maybe you\Ncould show me around?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514419,516119}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516119,517886}I really can?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517886,519652}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519652,522552}Awesome!\NI'll show you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523986,525986}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528719,531552}Takahiko lost his parents early.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531552,534952}As a result, he grew very selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536419,538019}I am sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538019,539919}Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545586,547452}Takahiko, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551252,553852}Incredible, Kyōta-niisan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564952,569186}Kiyohiko-niisan also liked to fish\Nand often went to this river.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569186,571186}Wait, you have a brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571186,573886}Yes. Unfortunately,\Nhe died three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583019,585619}Everything on this island\Nchanges beyond recognition,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.61,0:09:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585619,588986}but he had always\Nstayed the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588986,590586}Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596119,599552}Awesome!\NIt's a real knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599552,602119}Do you always have it\Nwith you, Kyōta-niisan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602119,605552}A lighter and a knife\Nare a must for every man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.55,0:10:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605552,607552}Holy cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621319,622919}Something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622919,625219}Looks like he fell off the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625219,627219}And then what?\NBitten by a wild dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627219,629119}Terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629119,631419}Oh, it's the Ikuhashi's boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633219,637419}Something horrible happened, lad.\NYour private teacher…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644852,649586}I don't know. Maybe there was\Nsome truth to his ghost stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649586,652119}Only a demon\Ncould do such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659686,662552}Get a grip.\NAre you a man or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662552,665152}Kyōta-niichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666886,669119}Oh, it's you guys.\NYou got here faster than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669919,671486}Faster? Very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671486,673786}How could you leave us\Nthere like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.78,0:11:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673786,676186}Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676186,680886}Takahiko, these are my younger\Nbrothers, Kyūta and Kyonta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680886,683219}You should get along easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.21,0:11:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683219,684786}Younger brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693652,699686}It was raining the day\Nyou first arrived here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:699686,701086}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701086,706352}I still remember my disbelief when\Nyou came and showed me the ashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708519,715252}My father was the only doctor on the island.\NI wanted to redeem his guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715252,717819}That's why I came to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:12:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717819,724386}Your father was a great doctor,\Nlike you are now, Kariya-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734052,739386}Ah, hell. Normally I am able\Nto sleep anywhere…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744019,745419}{\i1}A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745419,747119}{\i1}I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752886,755152}{\i1}It's the same aura as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766852,767852}{\i1}Takahiko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769186,770952}Serves you right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770952,773952}What is it, psychic?\NYou can't move?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775119,777586}{\i1}Takahiko has been possessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795986,797219}Kariya-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797219,801719}I am sorry to bother you at this hour, but\NI would like to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801719,804386}We will appreciate every hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804386,805386}Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808186,809852}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809852,812086}I feel hostile presence.\NIt's in the room above us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815319,821119}I will eliminate everyone\Nwho threatens my presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821119,823319}Just like that stupid beak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828586,830719}Stay away. Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831752,833452}Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846319,848386}Die, psychic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.38,0:14:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848386,850986}Say hello to Buddha from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851252,853986}{\i1}I have to summon…\NTakahiko's guardian spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866286,867786}Kiyohiko-niisan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873186,874719}Takahiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880952,881752}Is it over now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:892052,894652}Kyōta-niisan, I made you a toast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894652,895719}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895719,899319}What is he buttering up for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899319,900952}Would you like another coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900952,902219}Sure. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906719,909652}They seem to be have\Nbecome very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909652,912719}Who would have thought that such\Nan angel could be possessed by a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912952,915086}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915086,918119}What did you want to\Ntalk about last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:918119,920586}Ah, nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920586,926119}I heard your father once\Nran a clinic on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926119,928819}It is true. Old times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928819,933252}Time for a routine check-up.\NI must excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936952,939252}{\i1}I don't understand\Nsomething here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.01,0:15:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940019,943352}{\i1}Why was it only the siblings\Nthat committed these pseudo-suicides?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943352,947752}{\i1}Why would the soul of an\Ninnocent child hold such a grudge?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954586,955952}Mr. Genpei?\NAre you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957819,959319}Please hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960486,963519}I'll call a doctor in a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963519,966552}I don't think that's\Ngoing to be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012219,1013352}Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014886,1017286}Kyōta-niichan?\NDo you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017286,1019586}You look as if you got possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024552,1025552}Kyōta-niichan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029086,1031252}What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032819,1034586}Not good! Kyōta-niichan…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036552,1038119}What's going on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.11,0:17:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038119,1039719}Kyonta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040719,1042852}Kyūta-niichan!\NGeez, put something on yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042852,1045586}He almost killed me.\NClothing is now least important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045586,1048552}What? Killed? But by who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048952,1050386}Kyōta-niichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.38,0:17:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050386,1051586}You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051586,1055052}Listen, Kyonta.\NWe must join forces…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055052,1057119}…and call Kibatta-neechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064519,1067886}Kyōta! Or rather, the demon\Nwho disturbs the peace of this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069986,1073386}I came to get back the body of\Nmy younger brother from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073786,1075452}You stupid girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075452,1077886}I think someone is\Nunderestimating me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078619,1080886}– Show him what Pi-hyoro can do!\N– You can do it, Kibatta-neechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.88,0:18:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080886,1082552}Don't play with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095552,1098552}My brother is very strong.\NYou didn't choose your target very wisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099319,1102552}Enough of this nonsense, demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104852,1108052}Do you even have any idea\Nwhat you got yourselves into?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111452,1117052}One more step and your sweet brother\Nwill commit suicide right in front of your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117419,1119619}Go ahead.\NI'd love to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119619,1121119}Kibatta-neechan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121352,1125152}Damn. Don't regret\Nthose words later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125152,1126819}Kyōta-niichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135419,1138719}You disgusting humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139052,1141219}Who did he think he was?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.21,0:19:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141219,1143186}Kyōta-niichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143186,1144886}You must've been\Nworried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.88,0:19:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144886,1149519}But thanks to his possession,\NI could freely browse through his memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149519,1152586}– So you did it on purpose?\N– And here I was, losing my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152586,1155352}I thought so.\NIt was very like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155352,1158852}Tonight we will put an end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174252,1176252}I… I had a twin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176252,1178319}Yes. There is no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179252,1182319}But… how is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182786,1185952}There's more. It is his spirit\Nthat plagues this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188886,1193352}It was raining that night,\Njust like today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193352,1198352}My father was delivering you\Nand your twin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.35,0:20:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198352,1202852}It was a difficult delivery.\NYour mother died right after she gave birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203519,1205352}Soon after…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213219,1215352}My father got possessed\Nby an evil spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215719,1217386}An evil spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217386,1220919}Yes. It was a ghost seeking revenge\Non the Ikuhashi family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221486,1224886}My possessed father\Nstrangled Takahiko's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224886,1227619}A moment later,\Nhe regained consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.61,0:20:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227619,1230819}Is that what you wanted\Nto tell me last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230819,1232019}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.01,0:20:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232019,1235886}When he came to his senses,\Nhe couldn't believe the weight of his sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236019,1238719}It wasn't your father's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.71,0:20:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238719,1241919}The responsibility lies\Nwith the Ikuhashi family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242619,1247586}When I was young, I did a lot\Nof terrible things to create my wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1247586,1251119}To achieve my goals,\NI have ruined many lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251119,1254919}It was the only way\Nto survive in post-war Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:21:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254919,1260852}In my youth, I was a very proud man\Nand never bothered to look back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1260852,1264486}When Kariya-sensei came to\Nthe island with the ashes,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264486,1267752}when I heard about all this,\NI finally realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1267752,1271752}This is a punishment\Nfor my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271752,1276386}I lost my wife and my son,\Nand Kiyohiko soon joined them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276386,1279386}Now I have only Takahiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285619,1286419}He's here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.38,0:21:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289386,1292319}I almost had him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292719,1297119}I will not let these people\Ninterfere with my revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297819,1300086}– Your haunting ends here!\N– What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303286,1305652}Although connected to this world,\Nwe do not belong to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309286,1311652}Although connected to that world,\Nwe do not belong to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316319,1319186}Anger, revenge, malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.51,0:22:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322519,1326786}No matter what form evil takes,\Nwe shall get rid of it in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.21,0:22:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327219,1331786}The guardian deities of the modern world,\Nthe Pi-hyoro family is ready for action!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.78,0:22:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331786,1334286}We've come to send\Nyou to eternal rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339386,1343052}Do you have any idea who\Nyou're facing? I am a demon, fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.75,0:22:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1343752,1346019}Stop sinning any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.25,0:22:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1346252,1347619}Sinning?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1347619,1350786}I am but an embodiment\Nof Genpei's sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1350786,1354252}Try stopping me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.78,0:22:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1361786,1363486}Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1366219,1367752}Kyūta! Kyonta!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1369319,1373019}Kyōta, he may have a toddler's face,\Nbut he's strong. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.71,0:23:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1376719,1380986}Open your eyes, you moron! Who are you\Nactually trying to get revenge on?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1380986,1383519}What can you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1383986,1388819}Do you have any idea what it's like\Nto be killed without a chance to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.81,0:23:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1388819,1394519}How did I feel when I realized that it was\Nthe fault of the Ikuhashi family?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1396419,1402886}And that's supposed to justify killing\Nyour teacher and these innocent siblings?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.11,0:23:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1405119,1408319}Don't get close, Takahiko!\NThis baldie is not your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.88,0:23:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1408886,1411319}I didn't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.61,0:23:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1411619,1416786}Since you're here, Takahiko,\NI'll take you to hell with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.45,0:23:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1419452,1420852}Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1426286,1427652}Takahiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.65,0:23:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1427652,1428719}Ikuhashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.71,0:23:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1428719,1430619}Stop! Please spare him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.61,0:23:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1430619,1432486}It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.48,0:23:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1432486,1434619}Takahiko did nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.61,0:23:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1434619,1436686}You want me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.68,0:23:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1436686,1439686}What good will it do me\Nif you're dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.68,0:24:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1439686,1442552}No. I will rip everything\Nyou love out of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.05,0:24:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1446052,1448419}Takahiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.11,0:24:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1451119,1452419}Mr. Genpei!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.41,0:24:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1452419,1455152}You slimeball.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.51,0:24:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1459519,1461019}Please, stop it, little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.75,0:24:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1469752,1471019}Takahiko…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.01,0:24:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1471019,1477252}I've envied you and Kiyohiko-niisan\Nso much for your happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.61,0:24:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1492619,1494652}I knew nothing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1494652,1498986}If I were in his place,\NI'd probably do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.98,0:25:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1498986,1500752}Takahiko…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.75,0:25:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1500752,1503119}This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.21,0:25:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1510219,1513086}Good that we have each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.08,0:25:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1513086,1516919}Yes. I hope Takahiko\Nwill get better soon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.91,0:25:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1516919,1520052}Don't worry.\NHe didn't look like a softie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.05,0:25:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1520052,1521352}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.35,0:25:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1521352,1523919}I took the liberty of checking\Nwhat you really can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.71,0:25:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1524719,1528886}I was not disappointed,\NAvalokita Ema-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.58,0:25:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1529586,1530652}How do you know this name?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.75,0:25:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1532752,1534686}This aura…\NAre you from Chūkyō?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.65,0:25:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1537652,1539686}Is something wrong,\NKibatta-neechan?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.68,0:25:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1539686,1541519}No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.45,0:25:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1543452,1545586}{\i1}What is she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.88,0:25:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1547886,1553719}I showed up before Avalokita Ema-sama\Nand let her feel Chūkyō's aura, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.71,0:25:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1553719,1555586}Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.58,0:26:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1555586,1560852}Five Ninshū will penetrate\Ntheir timeline any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.85,0:26:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1560852,1566219}They will come after Pi-hyoro without a doubt.\NI leave matters in your hands, Kyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.78,0:26:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1566786,1567852}Yes, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.68,0:26:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1569686,1573219}{\i1}I am counting on you, Ema.
