Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.95,0:29:56.85,Default,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1791952,1796852}{\an8\fad(0,200)}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.11,0:29:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1794119,1798752}Who would've thought?! It's Christmas Eve\Nand Kyōta is going on his first date.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.75,0:30:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1798752,1802852}We are so glad. He's about\Nto finally find his happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.85,0:30:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1802852,1808152}However, it turns out to be\Na nasty trap set for our family!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.15,0:30:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1808152,1813786}The trap was laid by the Five Ninshū who fled\Nfrom Chūkyō. Now we have to face them!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.58,0:30:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1814586,1817786}Next time on the Guardian Deities:
